                        <p class="placename">
                Mukachevo Ghetto<br /><span class="alt">(Munkács Ghetto)</span>
            </p>
                                    <p class="municipality">
                <strong>Location:</strong>
                Mukachevo, Czechoslovakia<br />
                            </p>
                            <div>
                Ghetto established in April 1944 for the purpose of preparing the city&#39;s Jewish population for deportation. Most were deported to Auschwitz.
            </div>
